90
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:28,750
<font size="14"><b>{\an7}STONES: DE     FISH: D</b></font>

91
00:05:26,650 --> 00:05:28,750
<font size="14"><b>{\an7}NAME: ALLEN</b></font>

92
00:05:26,650 --> 00:05:28,750
<font size="14"><b>{\an7}AGE: 10</b></font>

93
00:05:26,650 --> 00:05:28,750
<font size="14"><b>{\an7}INVENTORY:</b></font>

94
00:05:26,650 --> 00:05:28,750
<font size="14"><b>{\an7}INSECTS D 30 COPIES    BEASTS D 30 COPIES   BIRDS    GRASS</b></font>

95
00:05:26,650 --> 00:05:28,750
<font size="14"><b>{\an7}STONES           FISH</b></font>

96
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is me at my very best...</font>

97
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">for right now, anyway.</font>

98
00:05:32,130 --> 00:05:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Say, Allen?</font>

99
00:05:33,250 --> 00:05:34,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes?</font>

100
00:05:34,380 --> 00:05:36,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Will you duel me with no holds barred?</font>

101
00:05:37,540 --> 00:05:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He didn't even need to ask.</font>

102
00:05:39,710 --> 00:05:41,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm out to win this year! Maximum effort!</font>

103
00:05:44,580 --> 00:05:45,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you.</font>

104
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Begin!</font>

105
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm twice as fast as last year!</font>

106
00:05:51,130 --> 00:05:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And I'm going straight for the win!</font>

107
00:05:59,580 --> 00:06:02,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Why can't I land a hit?
I should be faster than him!</font>

108
00:06:04,710 --> 00:06:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is he just reading all my moves?</font>

109
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dammit! It's my Sword Mastery skill!</font>

110
00:06:12,460 --> 00:06:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The level is too low!</font>

111
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He still hits like a truck!</font>

112
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Crap!</font>

113
00:06:24,330 --> 00:06:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The duel is over!</font>

114
00:06:27,290 --> 00:06:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I lost...</font>

115
00:06:29,420 --> 00:06:31,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I couldn't throw him off balance,
even with my superior speed.</font>

116
00:06:32,170 --> 00:06:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Did I need a bigger agility boost?</font>

117
00:06:33,710 --> 00:06:37,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No, he already overpowers me, so lowering
my attack stat would just make things worse...</font>

118
00:06:38,250 --> 00:06:40,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Granvelle huntsman doesn't disappoint.</font>

119
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You had me sweating there.</font>

120
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:45,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Right. Thank you for the...</font>

121
00:06:48,290 --> 00:06:49,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mihai.</font>

122
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You've put in hard work at the Academy
over the past three years.</font>

123
00:06:53,330 --> 00:06:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's clear from how skillful you've become.</font>

124
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you, Father.</font>

125
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're pretty tough, Allen!</font>

126
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Still no match for my brother, though.</font>

127
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Who are you to talk?</font>

128
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, hey! You should have Mihai
start giving you lessons now that he's back.</font>

129
00:07:10,250 --> 00:07:12,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I would love to learn from him!</font>

130
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:14,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, let me join in, too!</font>

131
00:07:15,250 --> 00:07:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cecil, Thomas.</font>

132
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I need to speak with you two.</font>

133
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What is it, Elder Brother?</font>

134
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I must leave to undertake the Noble's Duty.</font>

135
00:07:25,420 --> 00:07:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I won't be coming home anytime soon.</font>

136
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

137
00:07:29,080 --> 00:07:31,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm sorry. I know this comes as a surprise.</font>

138
00:07:31,790 --> 00:07:34,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hold on. What kind of duty is it?</font>

139
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm afraid I can't say...</font>

140
00:07:35,670 --> 00:07:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">When do you have to leave?</font>

141
00:07:37,670 --> 00:07:38,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Tomorrow.</font>

142
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Father?</font>

143
00:07:46,250 --> 00:07:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I was so excited to have you home again...</font>

144
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't fret. I'll be back in three years.</font>

145
00:07:53,710 --> 00:07:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Three years?!</font>

146
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:57,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It takes that long?</font>

147
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:58,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cecil...</font>

148
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't cry.</font>

149
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I see.</font>

150
00:08:02,630 --> 00:08:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's such a shame, Baron Granvelle.
Two of your three kids got saddled with a talent.</font>

151
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I seem to recall your eldest son
also had a talent, Viscount!</font>

152
00:08:12,380 --> 00:08:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You know how it goes.
We must fulfill the Noble's Duty.</font>

153
00:08:16,790 --> 00:08:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The baron knew this would happen all along.</font>

154
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Noble's Duty, huh?</font>

155
00:08:24,210 --> 00:08:25,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sounds ominous as hell.</font>

156
00:08:30,540 --> 00:08:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll be waiting for you
to come back, Elder Brother.</font>

157
00:08:33,790 --> 00:08:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thanks. See you later, Cecil.</font>

158
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're the pride of our family, son.</font>

159
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fulfill your duty and come back to us, okay?</font>

160
00:08:43,830 --> 00:08:44,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Right.</font>

161
00:08:52,130 --> 00:08:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Allen. Watch after Cecil for me.</font>

162
00:08:56,250 --> 00:08:57,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Keep her safe, okay?</font>

163
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? Uh, sure.</font>

164
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:07,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Farewell. I'm off to uphold the Granvelle name.</font>

165
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We'll miss you!</font>

166
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="44">Don't forget about us!</font>

167
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Felt like he was trembling.</font>

168
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Was it just my imagination?</font>

169
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:18,750
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ALLEN: AGE 10</b></font>

170
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:18,750
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}MAY OF THE FOLLOWING YEAR</b></font>

171
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've subjugated every goblin borough
in the area over the past six months.</font>

172
00:09:25,330 --> 00:09:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And now I'm level 35.</font>

173
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}NAME:           ALLEN</b></font>

174
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}AGE:</b></font>

175
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}TALENT:</b></font>

176
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}LEVEL:</b></font>

177
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}HP:</b></font>

178
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}MP:</b></font>

179
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ATTACK:</b></font>

180
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ENDURANCE:</b></font>

181
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}AGILITY:</b></font>

182
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}INTELLIGENCE:</b></font>

183
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:29,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}LUCK:</b></font>

184
00:09:28,290 --> 00:09:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The time is ripe.</font>

185
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,210
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}SKILLS:           SUMMON (5), CREATE (5), FUSE (5)</b></font>

186
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,210
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ENHANCE (5), EXPANSION (4), STORAGE, SHARE,</b></font>

187
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,210
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}DELETE, SWORD MASTERY (3), THROW (3)</b></font>

188
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,210
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}EXP:</b></font>

189
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ready up, team!</font>

190
00:09:32,130 --> 00:09:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's wreck this orc borough!</font>

191
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fillet's evasion boost is working wonders.
My guys are kicking ass one-on-one.</font>

192
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bron! Use Protect!</font>

193
00:09:45,170 --> 00:09:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Man, Bron comes in real clutch.</font>

194
00:09:47,170 --> 00:09:52,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I wonder if he's taking any damage? Not being able
to see the current HP of my summons is a problem.</font>

195
00:09:53,330 --> 00:09:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Although they can fight inexhaustibly,</font>

196
00:09:55,540 --> 00:09:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">they disappear without warning
after taking too much damage.</font>

197
00:09:58,630 --> 00:10:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Come on, Spidey! I need two more of you!</font>

198
00:09:58,710 --> 00:10:00,250
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}INSECT D</b></font>

199
00:09:58,710 --> 00:10:00,250
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}INSECT D</b></font>

200
00:09:58,710 --> 00:10:00,250
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ENDURANCE +20, AGILITY +20</b></font>

201
00:09:58,710 --> 00:10:00,250
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ENDURANCE +20, AGILITY +20</b></font>

202
00:10:00,830 --> 00:10:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lock down those archers!</font>

203
00:10:05,170 --> 00:10:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Perfect. Time to press our attack!</font>

204
00:10:16,580 --> 00:10:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Looks to be a hundred of 'em.
No, more like two hundred.</font>

205
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:22,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gimme all that delicious EXP!</font>

206
00:10:22,790 --> 00:10:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Take 'em down!</font>

207
00:10:26,790 --> 00:10:28,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Auxiliary team, get in there!</font>

208
00:10:29,290 --> 00:10:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hot damn! I'm practically swimming in EXP!</font>

209
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The plan is working great so far.</font>

210
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:38,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But the orcs are putting up more a fight
than the goblins did.</font>

211
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bron!</font>

212
00:10:45,790 --> 00:10:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What was that?!</font>

213
00:10:47,290 --> 00:10:48,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It must've been a spell.</font>

214
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:53,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is that an Orc King?
No, there should only be one of those.</font>

215
00:10:56,540 --> 00:11:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So, my first real look at magic in this world
is thanks to a monster?</font>

216
00:11:00,460 --> 00:11:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Funny, since I can't cast any myself.</font>

217
00:11:02,420 --> 00:11:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pro gamer mode on, baby.</font>

218
00:11:06,710 --> 00:11:07,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Brace for a second wave!</font>

219
00:11:08,330 --> 00:11:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Man, that's hot!</font>

220
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Damn. They hit my forces in the rear
where Bron can't cover.</font>

221
00:11:14,580 --> 00:11:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're gonna pay for that!</font>

222
00:11:16,210 --> 00:11:17,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Eat lead, sucker!</font>

223
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:21,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hell yeah! I can OHKO these fools!</font>

224
00:11:21,540 --> 00:11:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I have two steel balls left.</font>

225
00:11:23,170 --> 00:11:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I just need to not miss...</font>

226
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Uh, where'd they go?</font>

227
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dammit! They moved out of my range!</font>

228
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">These damn swine are smart!
They even know to aim for me.</font>

229
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:51,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is a scene straight outta Hell.
They've still got a hundred troops or so.</font>

230
00:11:52,210 --> 00:11:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I better quit playing defense
and make this a war of attrition.</font>

231
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've got plenty of D-rank magic stones.</font>

232
00:11:57,330 --> 00:11:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can summon more than 20,000 copies
of Teddy, if needed.</font>

233
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Plus, I've got 100 MP recovery items stocked up.</font>

234
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll just keep going until my MP runs dry.</font>

235
00:12:05,420 --> 00:12:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sic 'em, Teddy!</font>

236
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Great. The tide is slowly turning in my favor.</font>

237
00:12:21,830 --> 00:12:23,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cue boss battle music.</font>

238
00:12:24,130 --> 00:12:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Orc King is here!</font>

239
00:12:31,420 --> 00:12:34,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Did he just mow my guys down in one hit?
B-ranks are freakin' strong!</font>

240
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:37,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Create, Enhance, and Summon!</font>

241
00:12:40,380 --> 00:12:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Create, Enhance, and Summon!</font>

242
00:12:43,830 --> 00:12:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Create, Enhance, and Summon!</font>

243
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:49,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shit! I can't keep up!</font>

244
00:12:49,290 --> 00:12:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And Teddy can't even get close enough to attack!</font>

245
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bron! Use Protec-</font>

246
00:12:57,290 --> 00:12:58,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yikes!</font>

247
00:12:58,710 --> 00:13:00,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm in trouble! Bron's down!</font>

248
00:13:02,670 --> 00:13:03,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Teddy! Cover for me!</font>

249
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ow, that hurt...</font>

250
00:13:10,130 --> 00:13:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gotta recover my HP.</font>

251
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What now?</font>

252
00:13:15,830 --> 00:13:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How can I summon enough creatures to
overwhelm the boss while fending off those spells?</font>

253
00:13:20,250 --> 00:13:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I think I'm boned.</font>

254
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:24,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll just have to call it quits.</font>

255
00:13:24,380 --> 00:13:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Having a rough go of it, are we?</font>

256
00:13:33,040 --> 00:13:37,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}THE HARDCORE GAMER DOMINATES</b></font>

257
00:13:33,040 --> 00:13:37,040
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}IN ANOTHER WORLD WITH GARBAGE BALANCING</b></font>

258
00:13:37,830 --> 00:13:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Captain Zenof?!</font>

259
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How the hell? The knights shouldn't be here
until tomorrow at the earliest!</font>

260
00:13:44,290 --> 00:13:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All the smoke prompted me to come take a look.</font>

261
00:13:49,460 --> 00:13:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Care to explain?</font>

262
00:13:51,130 --> 00:13:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, I was hoping to wipe out the orc borough...</font>

263
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hmm.</font>

264
00:13:56,420 --> 00:13:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh crap. He's seen everything!</font>

265
00:13:58,130 --> 00:13:59,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Come back, everybody!</font>

266
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:06,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No comment on my summon creatures?</font>

267
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I shall slay the Orc King.</font>

268
00:14:10,710 --> 00:14:14,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You handle the other riff-raff,
Vice-Captain Leibrand.</font>

269
00:14:14,710 --> 00:14:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Understood, Captain.</font>

270
00:14:16,380 --> 00:14:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The Vice-Captain is here, too?!</font>

271
00:14:24,170 --> 00:14:27,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I would've liked some more EXP,
but this is just as good.</font>

272
00:14:28,250 --> 00:14:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A front row seat to a battle of aces!</font>

273
00:14:41,380 --> 00:14:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whoa!</font>

274
00:14:42,250 --> 00:14:45,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The captain earned a sobriquet from being
such a powerhouse on the battlefield.</font>

275
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">People call him: Zenof the War Demon.</font>

276
00:14:57,960 --> 00:15:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No way! He's parrying hits
from a monster twice his size!</font>

277
00:15:06,040 --> 00:15:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Magic orcs.</font>

278
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That explains where the fire is coming from.</font>

279
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What is that? Something similar
to Krena's Extra Skill?</font>

280
00:15:35,250 --> 00:15:37,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He was aiming for the magic orcs all along!</font>

281
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The vice-captain is just as OP as the captain!</font>

282
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How did he get his ass handed to him
by Krena that one time?!</font>

283
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Captain Zenof!</font>

284
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">H-holy shit...!</font>

285
00:16:17,380 --> 00:16:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He took out a B-rank monster
in one fell swoop? Without an Extra Skill?!</font>

286
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I didn't make it back home before nightfall.</font>

287
00:16:30,540 --> 00:16:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bet I'm getting yelled at again.</font>

288
00:16:33,130 --> 00:16:35,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I had a sneaking suspicion, but...</font>

289
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">you're the one who took out
the goblin nests, aren't you?</font>

290
00:16:40,380 --> 00:16:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah.</font>

291
00:16:43,580 --> 00:16:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Not long after you became
the Granvelle's manservant,</font>

292
00:16:47,420 --> 00:16:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I started hearing reports of monster carcasses
piling up outside the city.</font>

293
00:16:51,420 --> 00:16:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They had been stripped their magic stones.</font>

294
00:16:54,170 --> 00:16:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It wasn't very difficult to narrow down
who it could be,</font>

295
00:16:57,500 --> 00:17:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">given that you single-handedly hunted a White Deer
and even competed on par with Master Mihai.</font>

296
00:17:01,830 --> 00:17:03,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So, the jig is up, huh?</font>

297
00:17:04,330 --> 00:17:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You have a talent.</font>

298
00:17:06,830 --> 00:17:10,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Those animals who were fighting
alongside you are part of it, right?</font>

299
00:17:10,500 --> 00:17:13,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yep, that figures. My cover's totally blown.</font>

300
00:17:14,670 --> 00:17:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's right.</font>

301
00:17:17,210 --> 00:17:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm not admitting to any more than that.</font>

302
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's no telling what kind of mess
it'll make if I say anything</font>

303
00:17:22,460 --> 00:17:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">about being on talking terms
with the God of Creation.</font>

304
00:17:25,540 --> 00:17:28,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The baron already knows
you have a talent, by the way.</font>

305
00:17:29,250 --> 00:17:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's what motivated him
to promote you to Huntsman.</font>

306
00:17:32,290 --> 00:17:33,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I suppose that makes sense.</font>

307
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's unusual for a kid my age to be granted
so much freedom and responsibility.</font>

308
00:17:39,290 --> 00:17:40,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let me wipe you down.</font>

309
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Listen, Allen. If you wish me
to keep what I saw today a secret,</font>

310
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:48,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">then I shall leave it out
of my report to the baron.</font>

311
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:53,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But in exchange, I want you to keep me informed
on the progress of your monster hunts.</font>

312
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Our goals are one in the same, are they not?</font>

313
00:17:56,580 --> 00:18:01,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I shouldn't undercut the knights
just for the sake of farming more EXP.</font>

314
00:18:02,130 --> 00:18:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Right. As you wish.</font>

315
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:06,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've gotta say...</font>

316
00:18:06,830 --> 00:18:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm shocked this guy is still kicking.</font>

317
00:18:10,790 --> 00:18:15,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I mean, he's covered in battle scars
that never went away even after a level up.</font>

318
00:18:16,330 --> 00:18:19,290
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}2 WEEKS LATER</b></font>

319
00:18:19,290 --> 00:18:21,250
<font size="27" color="#ffffca"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE EARNED 25,000 EXP.</b></font>

320
00:18:19,290 --> 00:18:21,250
<font size="27" color="#ffffca"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE DEFEATED 1 ORC KING.</b></font>

321
00:18:20,250 --> 00:18:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sweet!</font>

322
00:18:21,460 --> 00:18:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mission complete! I've got it down
to a science now.</font>

323
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:32,790
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ORC BOROUGH</b></font>

324
00:18:25,630 --> 00:18:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">First, I attack from all sides
with a team of 40 Teddys.</font>

325
00:18:28,790 --> 00:18:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This puts a big dent into the orc forces
and prevents them from getting into formation.</font>

326
00:18:32,670 --> 00:18:35,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then I have my team target
the magic orcs until they're all dead.</font>

327
00:18:35,880 --> 00:18:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's a battle of numbers.</font>

328
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So long as I don't get attacked,
I can keep throwing summons at them until I win.</font>

329
00:18:43,130 --> 00:18:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The total EXP I earn from
an orc borough is... 335,000!</font>

330
00:18:47,380 --> 00:18:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's over seven times what I get
from a goblin one!</font>

331
00:18:50,080 --> 00:18:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Leverage a temporary failure
to achieve eventual success.</font>

332
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's the hardcore gamer way!</font>

333
00:18:56,210 --> 00:18:58,960
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ALLEN: AGE 10</b></font>

334
00:18:56,210 --> 00:18:58,960
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}SEPTEMBER</b></font>

335
00:18:59,080 --> 00:19:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We're honored to have you here.</font>

336
00:19:01,580 --> 00:19:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Good. Thank you for the warm welcome.</font>

337
00:19:04,040 --> 00:19:05,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A royal messenger, huh?</font>

338
00:19:08,670 --> 00:19:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">May I ask what brings you here today?</font>

339
00:19:11,540 --> 00:19:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I came to deliver this.</font>

340
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What am I looking at?</font>

341
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That is your son's diary.</font>

342
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Everyone is expected to write
periodic entries while at the barracks.</font>

343
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Please be aware that your son carried out
his mission dutifully and has been laid to rest.</font>

344
00:19:38,130 --> 00:19:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's not how this is supposed to go!</font>

345
00:19:40,420 --> 00:19:42,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How can such a thing happen in just six months?!</font>

346
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You people knew Mihai
was fresh out of the academy!</font>

347
00:19:46,580 --> 00:19:50,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can only assume you used him like fodder
because of our status as lower-ranking nobles!</font>

348
00:19:50,290 --> 00:19:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And is that a sentiment you wish for me
to share with the king?</font>

349
00:19:56,170 --> 00:19:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, Mihai...</font>

350
00:19:57,080 --> 00:19:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Milady!</font>

351
00:19:58,420 --> 00:20:01,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If you'll excuse us,
we have other places to visit today.</font>

352
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:03,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Farewell.</font>

353
00:20:07,670 --> 00:20:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I remember him acting strange that day...</font>

354
00:20:10,460 --> 00:20:13,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Allen. Watch after Cecil for me.</font>

355
00:20:14,670 --> 00:20:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Keep her safe, okay?</font>

356
00:20:18,040 --> 00:20:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Did he know he would die?!</font>

357
00:20:22,250 --> 00:20:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Father... what is going on?</font>

358
00:20:26,580 --> 00:20:28,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I need everyone else to clear the room first.</font>

359
00:20:29,290 --> 00:20:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Including you, Thomas.</font>

360
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? But why?!</font>

361
00:20:32,420 --> 00:20:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I want to know, too, Father!</font>

362
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:36,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Why only tell Cecil?</font>

363
00:20:41,170 --> 00:20:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Poor Master Mihai...</font>

364
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What? Are you telling me
you knew Mihai was going to die?!</font>

365
00:20:48,210 --> 00:20:51,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's part of a certain duty that we nobles
are expected to fulfill.</font>

366
00:20:51,170 --> 00:20:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And so what? The only reason
we're alive is to be killed for this duty?!</font>

367
00:20:56,080 --> 00:20:57,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's not like that.</font>

368
00:20:57,880 --> 00:20:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Listen...</font>

369
00:20:59,880 --> 00:21:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hold on, Cecil!</font>

370
00:21:10,580 --> 00:21:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So there's just nothing they can do?</font>

371
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is there some catch to being a noble
that forces them to adhere to this deadly duty?</font>

372
00:21:21,920 --> 00:21:24,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I hope that Lady Cecil is okay...</font>

373
00:21:25,170 --> 00:21:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She hasn't come out of her room since last night.</font>

374
00:21:27,710 --> 00:21:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">As I recall, the baron's parents and elder brother
also passed away at fairly young ages.</font>

375
00:21:34,130 --> 00:21:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All because of this "Noble's Duty" thing.</font>

376
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I don't get it. Losing your life at 15,
it's just too cruel...</font>

377
00:21:44,080 --> 00:21:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We need help! Lady Cecil is missing!</font>

378
00:21:47,080 --> 00:21:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lady Cecil!</font>

379
00:21:48,790 --> 00:21:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lady Cecil!</font>

380
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dammit. Some manservant I am!</font>

381
00:21:55,710 --> 00:21:57,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She climbed down from the window?!</font>

382
00:21:57,960 --> 00:21:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Have you found Cecil?</font>

383
00:21:59,460 --> 00:22:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">She might have left the estate.</font>

384
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm going to look outside!</font>

385
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll find her, no matter what!</font>

386
00:22:07,380 --> 00:22:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I just hope she doesn't do anything rash!</font>

